<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>TDYU haqqinda</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #0f2027, #203a43, #2c5364);
      color: white;
    }
    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 50px 20px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    header h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    section {
      padding: 40px 20px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #00c6ff;
    }
    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>TDYU – Tashkent Davlat Yuridik Universiteti</h1>
  <p>Keleshegingizni huquq penen baslan!</p>
</header>

<section>
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Universitet haqqinda</h2>
    <p>Toshkent Davlat Yuridik Universiteti – O'zbekistandagi en zor huquq maydanlarinin biri bolip esaplanadi. Bul jerde professional yuristler, advokatlar ham sudyalar tayyarlanadi.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Kiriw ushin ballari</h2>
    <p>TDYU ga kiriw ushin joqari ball talap qiladi. Ortasha 180+ ball jiynaw naslahed etiledi. Har jili ballar ozgerib turadi.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Kim boliw mumkin?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Advokat</li>
      <li>Sudya</li>
      <li>Prokuror</li>
      <li>Natarius</li>
      <li>Huquqshi</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Nege TDYU?</h2>
    <p>✔ Kushli bilim
    <br>✔ Zamanagoy sharayatlar
    <br>✔ Xalqara imkaniyatlar
    <br>✔ Juqari darejedegi ustazlar</p>
  </div>
</section>
</body>
</html>
